609
00:36:18,724 --> 00:36:21,126
Até Toothless e eu
encontro o Hidden World.

610
00:36:21,128 --> 00:36:23,660
Saia!

611
00:36:23,662 --> 00:36:25,129
Agora, sobre essa voz.

612
00:36:25,131 --> 00:36:28,600
Podemos perder a
coisa toda de buzina?

613
00:36:28,602 --> 00:36:30,834
